result.name: Paradise Classic

reviews.text:
Terrible service. Let's begin with waiting for a table. After waiting for 15 minutes, we asked how the progress on the table was. We received a rude and fierce response telling us it'll be our turn soon. 

Next, our waitress "tossed" dishes which made a loud clang when serving dishes on the table. Maybe she thought the dishes were Frisbees. 

Food wait time was decent albeit on the long side. Food tasted satisfactory. Overall, I wouldn't come back. Prices weren't cheap enough to warrant such poor service.
Highly recommend.  Reasonable price but really tasty.  5 heads tonight and all appreciated.

Southeast Asian style Chinese food. There are a lot of dishes and not much surprise, but decent quality and very reasonable price. Nothing to complain. I would have given it a 3.5 but add 0.5 star for the very fast speed in serving the dishes. The Laksa noodle soup is worth trying and pretty authentic.

Great quality Cantonese food, quick service, attentive staff, popular lunch destination and therefore very busy you might have to wait 5-10 mins for a table. They usually have half price offer during lunch so definitely worth trying it!
Not a restaurant I would recommend if you are looking for Singapore food. If you come here for a quick lunch (with 50% off) then it is all good.

result.name: 樂天經典

reviews.text: 至愛辣椒蟹👍🏻
食物質素比開張前差晒，正價時段價錢較貴，份量一般都比前縮晒水，味道較濃，口感及餸菜味道比一年之前差咗， 食市一般詬病，換走咗D大厨，剩返D二三厨及散仔，變成偷工減料質素大降，下午茶時段D食材更差,肉丸米線D肉似是煲完湯既肉,😖或過期雪藏肉味道,味精湯底搭夠,已食不到開張時之原有南洋風味，將貨就價！希望…🤔…………～極待改善～改善～

第一次來吃晚餐，體驗很差。
食物來齊吃完時一刻，我正在看單菜單，有待應走來收捨枱面，問：食物來齊了嗎？
都齊了不如結帳地催促。

那個催促的動作首先我很討厭，不是因為價錢問題，規定用饍時間是90mins，我並不是設計時器刻意留到最黎一刻的人。
也不是因為身旁的左一對夫妻，右一對夫妻沒有相同被如此對討。
首先我負100，他負600，大家也是來光顧的，我接受商業角度對消費能力高的人展示較好的待遇。
但那不是我的注點，我不認為消費多便可以無理要求。

但他的動作如像拒絕顧客，因為我還在看menu。
即是我有可能再點餐，沒有店鋪會拒絕做生意機會，除非你是麻煩的客人。或長遠看會損害利益。

因為我們只吃了40mins，期間沒有不合理要求。
當你看見客人在看menu，在確認食物已經到齊後，應該先禮貌詢問還要下單嗎，而並不是：不如同你埋單！
最好改成：如果沒有其它需要，不如同你埋單，好不好？
必需清晰表達給予客人選擇和拒絕的空間。
而不是催促人，讓人感覺你的待遇有偏差。

剛坐下，茶又沒開職員便走開。
到首次下單才開茶，只有香片，普洱。

食物品質過得去。

Terrible service. Let's begin with waiting for a table. After waiting for 15 minutes, we asked how the progress on the table was. We received a rude and fierce response telling us it'll be our turn soon. 

Next, our waitress "tossed" dishes which made a loud clang when serving dishes on the table. Maybe she thought the dishes were Frisbees. 

Food wait time was decent albeit on the long side. Food tasted satisfactory. Overall, I wouldn't come back. Prices weren't cheap enough to warrant such poor service.
大家樂質素。 70蚊一個餸用啫喱兜上。 胡椒湯買相似例湯。 上菜次序全錯， 涼菜最後上， 炒飯第一個上。
